title: I Wasn’t Left, I Lingered (Stephen Chandler)
description:
If God hasn't revealed what's next, He may still have something to show you right now. In “I Wasn’t Left, I Lingered,” Pastor Stephen Chandler of Union Church teaches us how to stay focused on our purpose when we feel like we should be further along.

If you’ve just made a decision for Christ, please respond HERE: http://ele.vc/tIepfr
